<div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 text-center lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-xs flex-col gap-y-4">
        <div class="mx-auto">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="50" height="50" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-file-earmark-person " viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M11 8a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0"/>
            <path d="M14 14V4.5L9.5 0H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2M9.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 11 4.5h2v9.255S12 12 8 12s-5 1.755-5 1.755V2a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <dd class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">35 Clientes satisfechos</dd>
        <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-400">Personas y empresas que confiaron en mis servicios.</dt>
        </div>
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-xs flex-col gap-y-4">
        <div class="mx-auto">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="50" height="50" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-sort-up-alt" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M3.5 13.5a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0V4.707L1.354 5.854a.5.5 0 1 1-.708-.708l2-1.999.007-.007a.5.5 0 0 1 .7.006l2 2a.5.5 0 1 1-.707.708L3.5 4.707zm4-9.5a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h1a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h5a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1zM7 12.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h7a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1h-7a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <dd class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">50 Proyectos completados</dd>
        <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-400">Trabajos entregados con éxito en distintas áreas de diseño y desarrollo.</dt>     
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-xs flex-col gap-y-4">
        <div class="mx-auto">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="50" height="50" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-person-lines-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M6 8a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6m-5 6s-1 0-1-1 1-4 6-4 6 3 6 4-1 1-1 1zM11 3.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-4a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5m.5 2.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h4a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1zm2 3a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h2a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1zm0 3a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h2a.5.5 0 0 0 0-1z"/>
          </svg>   
        </div>
        <dd class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Colaboraciones destacadas</dd>
        <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-400">Alianzas con marcas y profesionales para crear proyectos de alto impacto.</dt>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>
